p.k: The Granny Trap The kids discover that Nevin’s Granny Grancie has an estranged sister/best friend, Granny Grindle. Nevin and Lil’ Lemon, with Seth’s help, vow to reunite them!
p.d: This prehistoric comedy from Stephen Neary explores Fungietown through the whimsical quests of Seth, a young student at Fungietown Elementary.
